---
title: Chicken and Pepper Fajita Bowl with Coriander Rice, Tomato Salsa and Soured Cream
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chicken and Pepper Fajita Bowl in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220812_R16_W39_UK_QR11399-16_KB_Main_8_low-072054d1.jpg
